ies in Data Science with numerous top organizations like Google, Amazon, Deloitte and more, ready to pay high packages have set the domain on fire making it the hottest tech domains to learn. Data Science training is considered essential for all graduates, professionals and fresher folks who are looking for a career as a Data Scientist.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services offers an array of summer training courses delivered through industry experts who are focused at imparting the much demanded Data Science analytical skills through live industry projects, making you readily employable at global organizations.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Data Science Summer Training Benefits @ Brillica Services</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n6 weeks of intensive Data Science summer training program in Dehradun at Brillica Services’ premises offers you the following advantages:\r\n<br><br> \r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        Personal Training assistance from certified mentors</li>\r\n    <li>Chance to work on live industry-projects</li>\r\n<li>Access to expertly-curated curriculum</li>\r\n<li>   Opportunity to get trained from top academicians and industrialists</li>\r\n<li>   Great opportunity to gain proficient data science skills from your fellow peers</li>\r\n<li>   Boost your profile strength thereby providing a higher level of opportunities</li>\r\n<li>    Chance to get hired as interns at esteemed organizations</li>\r\n<li>    Recognized certificate of completion and much more…\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>\"Invest your time and efforts this summer in learning Data Science technologies at Brillica Services and secure your future!!\"</b>\r\n', '3rd March 2020'),
(5, 'img/pmp.jpg', '', 'PMP FAQ’s: All That You Must Know About How to Prepare for the New PMP Exam', 'Staying ahead of the competition and surviving in the global economy form the core motives, turning the organizations to project management, with a tenet to attain consistent growth in business results. The global organizations believe that a disciplined approach to the project, portfolio and program management can deliver the expected business value at every stage, leading to investing significantly on hiring project management experts and leverage greater efficiency, enhanced stakeholder faith and satisfaction. PMP certification is the key to it that can help you unlock an array of project management career opportunities and acquiring critical management skills. So, What is PMP certification all about, its eligibility criteria, exam format and how to prepare for PMP Certification exam and many other queries stand answered in this blog.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>What is PMP?</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nPMI (Project Management Institute) offers the globally renowned certification, known as PMP (Project management Professional), that is acclaimed as a standard measure of the project management competencies. Acquiring PMP certification credentials are prestigious for project managers to validate the cutting-edge skills to plan, organize, implement, control all project phases and efficiently managing resources, stakeholders, time and efforts driving projects to success.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Who can take PMP certification?</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nProject Management Professional certification can be aimed by experienced project managers who:\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>\r\n    Shoulder the responsibility of executing projects under supervision and are familiar with all aspects of the project lifecycle\r\n</li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li>\r\n    Lead the project teams and direct them to adhere to project deadlines and simultaneously adhere to a defined budget, schedule and resources\r\n</li>\r\n<br>\r\n<li>\r\n    Demonstrate pertinent knowledge of applying the suitable methodology of executing clearly defined projects.\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>\r\n    What is the pre-requisite to take PMP certification Exam?\r\n</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nTaking the PMP certification exam requires you to qualify one of the listed criteria completely:\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        A high school diploma, an associate degree, or its equivalent with a minimum of 5 years of project management experience constituting 7,500 hours in leading project tasks and 35 hours of PMP training classes.</li>\r\n<li>A 4-year educational degree with at least 3 years of experience in project management founding 4,500 hours of leading projects and 35 hours of formal PMP certification training.\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<b>What is the format of the PMP Exam?\r\n\r\n</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe current PMP exam format is based on 5 performance domains and contains 200 multiple choice questions that need to be answered in 4 hours.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe exam questions are segregated into 5 process groups based on PMBOK Guide, to test your practical approach of handling complex project situations:\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        Initiation (13%)</li>\r\n\r\n<br><li>Planning (24%)</li>\r\n<br><li>Executing (30%)</li>\r\n<br><li>Monitoring and Controlling (25%)</li>\r\n<br><li>Closing (8%)\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>But according to the PMI announcement regarding the recent PMP certification changes, from 1st July 2020, the PMP exam would be based    \r\n      on 3 domains including:</b>\r\n      <br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li><b>People (42%)</b></li>\r\n    <br><li><b>Process (50%)</b></li>\r\n    <br><li><b>\r\n        Business Environment (8%)</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Is the PMBOK Guide also changing?</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nNo, PMP certification and training programs would continue to follow the PMP bible PMBOK 6th edition in the same way as the seventh edition is not expected to be out before 2023. The change is to be brought into the ways how to prepare for PMP exam considering the new format and the tested modules.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>What is the passing criteria for PMP certification?</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe PMP certification measures and scores your understanding as:\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        Proficient</li>\r\n<br><li>Moderately Proficient</li>\r\n<br><li>Below Proficient\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\nBased on the achieved proficiency levels in all domains an overall performance report is generated that defines your result. There are no specific criteria related to a minimum or maximum domains you need to attain the proficient levels to pass the PMP exam. \r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>How many PMP Exam retakes can be taken?</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou can retake the PMP exam thrice in one year. Based on the score report, generated after submitting the exam, you can analyze your proficiency level for all the performance domains and prepare accordingly before retaking the exam to save on the cost and efforts.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>How to prepare for PMP?</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nPreparing for PMP certification exam requires you to have profound understanding and approach to\r\n implementing the project management knowledge areas, processes in different project stages, that \r\n can be achieved by enrolling into PMI authorized training centre offering extensive PMP training\r\n  and certification courses. The PMBOK sixth edition based <b>PMP training classes</b>, delivered by \r\n  industry experts can help you prepare and pass the tough exam with striking scores.<b>The project \r\n    management professional training classes are made available to you \r\n  in</b> blended learning modes that can be customized to meet your specific learning needs.\r\n\r\n  <br><br>\r\n  <b>Should you take the PMP Exam before or after the 2020 Update?</b>\r\n  <br><br>\r\n\r\n  Before July 2020 is always advisable for all those who are already taking PMP training classes and preparing for the PMP exam from long, because, after July, it is certainly going to be tougher.\r\n<br><br>\r\nUsually, it takes 8 -10 weeks to get trained and self-study the learnt PMP fundamentals. So, if you are reading this, you still have to take the chance and achieve the most prestigious PMP credentials now. Brillica Services can help you get closer to your career goal through extensive PMP training and certification course as we understand that your opportunity window is getting smaller day by day.', '28th February 2020'),
(6, 'img/pythonmachinelearn.png', '', 'Project-Based Summer Training in Python & Machine Learning in Dehradun, Uttarakhand', 'Are you an engineering graduate or pursuing it and aiming to enter the tough job-market full of neck to neck competition with your academic knowledge?\r\n<br><br>\r\nWell, it is certainly not enough, because we have thousands of engineering students parallel to you with the same knowledge and competencies. However, one thing that can set you apart is only “hands-on experience”! Today all organizations prefer hiring those students who are technically sound, creative and analytical and who can start performing from day one. They do not want to invest their resources in training you before putting you to work. Therefore, A quality solution to this is undertaking project-based summer training to validate your practical knowledge and technical expertise over a specific technology.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Why take Project-Based Summer Training in Python and Machine Learning</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Importance of Python and Machine Learning</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nIT industry in India has shown phenomenal growth in the last decade. With innovative technologies evolving every day, the Indian IT industry is set to become the fastest-growing market globally in the next ten years. Being an engineering student, you must not be confined to only theoretical knowledge, but also have an idea about the acute details of latest technologies, its applications and scope in the future. Every engineering student now is capable enough to understand the importance of building hands-on projects. More projects in your profile, more capable you are in the eyes of the recruiter. Your projects speak louder than your college marks and certainly give you an upper hand during the process of placements.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOf the emerging technologies, Python and Machine Learning have seen unprecedented growth in popularity, recognition, career and scope. For this reason, most of the engineering students are investing their crucial summer training break into <b>project-based summer training in Python and Machine Learning</b>.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Amazing Python and Machine Learning growth facts</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>According to IBM, Python is the most popular language for machine learning</li>\r\n<br><li>The market size of Machine Learning is expected to grow from $1.41 Billion in 2017 to $ 8.81 Billion by 2022, at a Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) of 44.1%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br><br>\r\nKnowing these, who would miss on the opportunity to make a career into the booming domain of Python and Machine Learning?\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>What’s so unique about Project-based summer training in Python and machine learning in Dehradun?</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nOver the years the trends have revealed that Dehradun has become a most desirable place to stay and learn for young technocrats as the place is blessed with the scenic beauty of nature and pleasant climate and is surrounded by esteemed engineering colleges. Preparing you for the growing industry with a wide array of course choices on emerging technologies, Brillica Services is one of the pioneering technology training institutes that believe in learning through project implementations.\r\n<br><br>\r\nMost engineering students having a knack for programming and aspiration to carve careers in Artificial Intelligence domain choose project-based summer training in <b>Python and Machine Learning at Brillica Services in Dehradun</b>.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>It is a 6-week course where the curriculum is concentrated on instilling in-depth knowledge and understanding of practical implications of the learnt concepts through live industry projects. Such extensive and expertly curated course helps you become job-ready and upfront the corporate challenges fearlessly.</li>\r\n<br><li>Exhaustive project-based summer training at Brillica Services acclaims to make readily employable with the industry-relevant Python and machine learning skills by developing a broad industry outlook. Constant inclusion of beginner to advanced level <b>python and machine learning projects in the summer training here in Dehradun</b> helps you step ahead in your learning and career journey progressively.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br><br>\r\nBesides the above factors, other reasons to seriously pursue the Python and Machine Learning summer training program is to:\r\n<br><br>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n    <li>\r\n        Gain in-depth technical knowledge of the Python language, functions libraries and understand how it applies to the machine learning algorithms.</li>\r\n<br><li>Enhance technical skills in a real-time environment.</li>\r\n<br><li>Take a deep dive into the specialized machine learning projects, algorithms and chase your area of interest by gaining specialization gradually.</li>\r\n<br><li>Develop skills to work in a team.</li>\r\n<br><li>Improve awareness of the industrial environment and work culture of the Python and machine learning industry.</li>\r\n<br><li>Develop an analytical approach to build real-time machine learning projects using Python codes.</li>\r\n<br><li>Interact with industry experts; seek constant mentoring and guidance to resolve queries with practical exposure.</li>\r\n<br><li>6-week project-based summer training Certificate from Brillica Services adds strength to your profile and resume as the courses are recognized.</li>\r\n<br><li>Open doors to job opportunities in reputed tech organizations exhibiting your skills and knowledge.</li>\r\n<br><li>Projects during summer training help in validating your core Python and machine learning competencies making it easier for the future employers to judge your capabilities and skills.\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Closing Thoughts</b>\r\n<br><br>\r\nIf you have made your mind and are really serious about your career then you must not waste your precious summer vacations this year in bluffing your seniors by purchasing ready-made projects, instead take up the 6-week summer training in Python and machine learning in Dehradun at Brillica Services, that makes it non-tedious yet engaging for you. Our certified industry experts specialize in instilling in you the most sought-after python and machine learning through live industry-projects that help you get acquainted with the industry scenarios, challenges and ways to resolve it analytically.', '26th February 2020 ');
