(12, 'Microsoft Azure Training', 'Microsoft Azure is the scalable and highly available platform offering extensive cloud services for IT professionals and developers to design, architect, develop, deploy and efficiently manage diverse cloud applications and services. Empowered with datacenter network across the globe, Azure provides DevOps support and various integrated tools to build simple to complex cloud solutions.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>Microsoft Azure Infrastructure and Deployment Track</li>\r\n<li>Microsoft Azure Integration and Security Track</li>\r\n<li>Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Microsoft Azure Solutions Architect Technologies Track</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Microsoft Azure Solutions Architect Design Track/li>\r\n\r\n<li>Microsoft Azure Solutions Architect Design Track</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', '', 'Microsoft Azure is the scalable and highly available platform offering extensive cloud services for IT professionals and developers to design, architect, develop, deploy and efficiently manage diverse cloud applications and services. Empowered with datacenter network across the globe, Azure provides DevOps support and various integrated tools to build simple to complex cloud solutions. This intuitive platform offers a wide range of services including analytics, computing, databases, networking, storage and web &amp; mobile applications.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services provides an array of Microsoft', 'Azure certification courses to help cloud developers, administrators and engineers to acquire hands-on experience in Azure cloud computing. Our comprehensive and all-encompassing Azure training and certification courses are available as instructor-led and e-learning modes allowing the aspiring professionals to choose one as per their preference and schedule.\r\n<br><br>\r\nYou can now learn Azure from the industry experts and certified trainers at Brillica Services and achieve an in-depth understanding of the Azure cloud at the most reasonable cost and custom training schedules in your favourite mode of training.', '', 'System and Network Administrators,\r\nSystem and application developers,\r\nInfrastructure managers,\r\nDevOps Engineers,\r\nand all IT professionals who have a knack to learn Microsoft Azure cloud computing', 3, 'img/group 2313@3x.jpg'),
(13, '\r\nCertified Scrum Master Training', 'Scrum is one of the most popular and highly-demanded agile methodologies that help to execute projects flawlessly with swift workflows based on agile principles.  The Certified Scrum Master Certification (CSM) validates your expertise in implementing agile practices effortlessly.\r\n\r\n', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li> Agile and Scrum Overview</li>\r\n<li>The three roles in Scrum</li>\r\n<li>Scrum Ceremonies</li>\r\n<li>Scrum Artifacts</li>\r\n<li>Sprint Execution</li>\r\n<li>Daily Scrum and Sprint Retrospective</li>\r\n<li>Definition of Done (DoD) and Acceptance Criteria</li>\r\n<li>Definition of Ready</li>\r\n<li>Release Planning</li>\r\n<li>Sprint Burndown Chart</li>\r\n<li>Release Burn-Up Chart</li>\r\n<li>Product Planning</li>\r\n<li>User Stories</li>\r\n<li>Agile Estimation</li>\r\n<li>Planning Poker  </li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n', 'There are no official pre-requisites to attend the ScrumMaster Certification course and it can be taken by any professional who wants to excavate Scrum essentials and attain expertise in Scrum.', 'Scrum is one of the most popular and highly-demanded agile methodologies that help to execute projects flawlessly with swift workflows based on agile principles.  The Certified Scrum Master Certification (CSM) validates your expertise in implementing agile practices effortlessly. The CSM certification training is designed to solidify the agile fundamentals, understand the Scrum framework, execute scrum in projects, manage scrum teams effectively and embed changes, as and when required.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services is a leading provider of Scrum Master Certification training and helps evolve project manager professionals into', 'Scrum masters. Our certified and experienced instructors are dedicated to impart intensive CSM training and carve catalysts that can assure effective Scrum panel integration into the project environment and achieve desired project outcomes.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe CSM certification training course at Brillica Services help you comprehend the basics of Scrum and the Scrum lifecycle, organize Scrum team and implement a Scrum, from releases and sprints and set the stage for the project execution to enterprise transformation.  ', '', 'Software Engineers,\r\nProduct Managers,\r\nProject Managers,\r\nTeam Leaders,\r\nBusiness Analysts,\r\nDevelopment team members,\r\nTesters,\r\nNew/Existing Scrum Masters,\r\nPlanning for Scrum Master career,\r\nAll Scrum team members such as developers, Scrum Masters, and product owners,\r\nand all professionals who would like to pursue a career as a professional Scrum Master.', 4, 'img/group 2312.png'),
(14, '\r\nPMI-ACP Training', 'The PMI Agile Certified Practitioner (PMI-ACP)® Certification course authenticates your knowledge on implementing agile techniques, methodologies, and principles. PMI-ACP® certification is focused on sharpening skills on integrating application-based agile methodologies such as Kanban, Scrum, Lean and test-driven development (TDD) successfully in the enterprise environment.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>  Agile Principles and Mindset\r\n   </li>\r\n\r\n<li> Value-driven delivery\r\n   </li>\r\n\r\n<li>Stakeholder management\r\n   </li>\r\n\r\n<li> Team performance\r\n   </li>\r\n\r\n<li> Adaptive planning\r\n   </li>\r\n\r\n\r\n<li> Problem detection and resolution\r\n   </li>\r\n\r\n<li>Tools and Techniques\r\n   </li>\r\n\r\n<li>Communication management</li>\r\n<li>Facilitation methods</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge sharing/written communication</li>\r\n<li>Leadership</li>\r\n<li>Building agile teams</li>\r\n<li>Team motivation</li>\r\n<li>Physical and virtual co-location\r\nGlobal, cultural, and team diversity\r\nTraining, coaching, and mentoring ∙</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'You may need a secondary degree or higher, or\r\n2000 hours of general project management experience in the last five years or\r\nAt least 1,500 hours of experience working on agile project teams during the last three years.\r\n', 'The PMI Agile Certified Practitioner (PMI-ACP)® Certification course authenticates your knowledge on implementing agile techniques, methodologies, and principles. PMI-ACP® certification is focused on sharpening skills on integrating application-based agile methodologies such as Kanban, Scrum, Lean and test-driven development (TDD) successfully in the enterprise environment. The PMI-ACP training and certification mapped course is aimed to instil across-the-board project management acumen, essential to execute them with efficacy and agility.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe PMI-ACP training course at Brillica Services', ' is designed to help existing management professionals solidify their management expertise, exercise the learnt agile best practices and increase industry value on the go. The brilliant team constituted of certified and experienced instructors at Brillica Services is dedicated to impart an in-depth understanding of the agile tools and enhance your collaboration skills.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrilica Services offers you a plethora of training options in the form of instructor-led classroom and online training modes, schedules and location to address your preferred learning specifications effectively.\r\n\r\n', '', 'Project managers,\r\nTeam leads/managers,\r\nProject executives/engineers,\r\nSoftware developers,\r\nAgile team members,\r\nAssociate/asst. manager – projects,and\r\nany professional aspiring to be a project manager', 4, 'img/group 2312.png');
