(15, '\r\nSAFe Certification Training', 'Fostering enterprise growth with the steep rise in productivity, SAFe ( Scaled Agile Framework) is an all-inclusive methodology that helps all project leaders and change managers in facilitating teams with increased collaboration and agility. At all project phases, it is important to apply and confirm adherence to Agile practices', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li> Introduction to the Scaled Agile Framework (SAFe®)</li>\r\n<li> Embracing a Lean-Agile Mindset</li> \r\n<li> Implementing an Agile Release Train\r\nLeading the Lean-Agile Enterprise</li>\r\n<li>Implementing Lean Portfolio Management</li>\r\n<li>Understanding SAFe® Principles\r\nExperiencing PI Planning</li>\r\n<li>Executing and Releasing Value\r\nBuilding an Agile Portfolio</li>\r\n<li>Coordinating Large Value Streams</li>\r\n<li>Establishing Team and Technical Agility</li>\r\n<li>Experiencing Program Increment (PI) Planning</li>\r\n<li>Releasing on Demand with DevOps\r\nBuilding Business Solutions and Lean Systems   </li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'All individual can take this course but it is highly recommended if you have 5+ years of experience in software development, testing, business analysis, product or project management and\r\nExperience in Scrum.', 'Fostering enterprise growth with the steep rise in productivity, SAFe ( Scaled Agile Framework) is an all-inclusive methodology that helps all project leaders and change managers in facilitating teams with increased collaboration and agility. At all project phases, it is important to apply and confirm adherence to Agile practices. The SAFe framework provides the highest level of synchronization, alignment and alliance amongst team members, ensuring quality-driven deliveries and enterprise success.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services helps you become the change agent ', 'and scale your Agile efforts at an enterprise level through its extensive SAFe training and certification course. Our certified and experienced instructors are focused on instilling the expertise to understand and enforce the Lean-Agile mindset, apply learnt agile principles, execute program portfolio management and coordinate large value streams in the organization. \r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services offers you blended learning modes to take the SAFe training course at your convenience. The SAFe training and certification course from Brillica Services can help you widen your career scope and lead Lean-Agile enterprises on the go.', '', 'Program & Project Managers,\r\nProduct & Product Line Managers,\r\nDevelopment, QA & Infrastructure Managers,\r\nPortfolio Managers, PMO & Process Leads\r\nEnterprise, System & Solution Architects\r\nExecutives and Leaders, Managers, Directors, CIOs & VPs.\r\n', 4, ''),
(17, '\r\nCAPM Training', 'PMI’s CAPM ( Certified Associate in  Project Management) Certification is a globally accredited certification that helps budding project managers to demonstrate project managerial skills to best-fit the project and organization environment. It is specifically designed for project management beginners to empower them with a holistic overview of core management philosophies, process groups and knowledge areas encompassed in PMBOK and prescribed by PMI', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li> Introduction to CAPM </li>\r\n<li> Introduction to Project Management </li>\r\n<li> Project Environment</li>\r\n<li> Role of the Project Manager</li>\r\n<li> Project Integration Management </li>\r\n<li>  Project Scope Management </li>\r\n<li> Project Schedule Management </li>\r\n<li>  Project Cost Management </li>\r\n<li>  Project Quality Management </li>\r\n<li>  Project Resource Management</li>\r\n<li>  Project Resource Management </li>\r\n<li>  Project Communication Management</li>\r\n<li> Project Risk Management </li>\r\n<li>Project Procurement Management</li>\r\n<li>Project Stakeholder Management</li>\r\n</ul>', '\r\nThe course does not have any official pre-defined pre-requisite to taking the course. ', 'PMI’s CAPM ( Certified Associate in  Project Management) Certification is a globally accredited certification that helps budding project managers to demonstrate project managerial skills to best-fit the project and organization environment. It is specifically designed for project management beginners to empower them with a holistic overview of core management philosophies, process groups and knowledge areas encompassed in PMBOK and prescribed by PMI.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services is a pioneering IT training company', 'to impart high-end CAPM training experience. Our expert-led classes and curriculum are targeted to instil a thorough understanding of the project management fundamentals, processes, underlying principles and best practices. We help you attain distinguished project management skills vital to have a promising career in the project management domain.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOur custom training solutions and blended learning modes help you attain the much demanded CAPM training based on your specific learning preferences at affordable costs.', '', 'Project associates and executives,\r\nAny professional aspiring to start a career in project management\r\n', 5, ''),
(18, '\r\nCBAP Training', 'CBAP(Certified Business Analysis Professional) Certification endorsed by IIBA is the third level certification, designed for individuals possessing extensive experience in business analysis domain.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>CBAP Course Introduction</li>\r\n<li>Key Concepts and terminologies</li>\r\n<li>CBAP Knowledge Areas</li>\r\n<li>Business Analysis Planning and Monitoring</li>\r\n<li>Elicitation and Collaboration/li>\r\n<li>Requirements Lifecycle Management</li>\r\n<li>Strategy Analysis</li>\r\n<li>Requirements Analysis and design definition</li>\r\n<li>Solution Evaluation</li>\r\n<li>Underlying Competencies</li>\r\n<li>Techniques</li>\r\n<li>Agile Perspective</li>\r\n<li>Business Intelligence Perspective</li>\r\n<li>Information Technology Perspective</li>\r\n<li>Business Architecture Perspective</li>\r\n<li>Business Process Management Perspective</li>\r\n<li>CBAP exam taking strategy</li>\r\n</ul>', 'As per the official pre-requisites, the IIBA-CBAP® course requires minimum 7500 hours of work experience in the last 10 years, of which 900 hours should be in 4 knowledge areas defined in BABOK® Guide. Along with this, you must have 35 hours of Professional Development (PDs) in the past four years.', '\r\nCBAP(Certified Business Analysis Professional) Certification endorsed by IIBA is the third level certification, designed for individuals possessing extensive experience in business analysis domain. CBAP is a universally recognized certification that demonstrates your mastery in business analysis, advanced documentation, effective planning, and devising flawless business solutions. The CBAP course foundation is laid with the comprehensive concepts encompassed in BABOK official guide.\r\n<br><br>\r\nThe CBAP training at Brillica Services is envisioned to help you acquire the industry’s most embraced business analysis', 'skill set and allows you to take a career leap. Our team of certified instructors helps you gain an across-the-board understanding of the included six knowledge areas and core concept model of business analysis, important from the CBAP exam perspective.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services is a premier training company to offer a perfect blend of diverse training modes to help you master CBAP technology and included business analysis approach.  Our readily available custom schedules for the instructor-led classroom, on-line, group, private and onsite training, make it more enriching for CBAP certification seeking professionals to select the most feasible training solution based-on their preferences.\r\n\r\n', '', 'The IIBA® Certified Business Analysis Professional (CBAP®) certification course is ideal for business analysts with seven to ten years of experience, senior analysts and project managers', 5, ''),
(19, 'CCBA Training', 'The Certification of Capability in Business Analysis (CCBA) certification is designed to empower business analyst professionals, with cutting edge business analysis skills, trusted worldwide to devise perfect business solutions and produce reliable quality results. Based on the industry standards.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li> \r\nIntroduction to CCBA certification   \r\n</li>\r\n\r\n<li> \r\nIntroduction to BABOK V3  \r\n</li>\r\n<li> \r\n Business Analysis Planning and Monitoring  \r\n</li>\r\n<li> \r\n Elicitation and Collaboration   \r\n</li>\r\n<li> \r\nIRequirements Life Cycle Management  \r\n</li>\r\n<li> \r\n Strategy Analysis  \r\n</li>\r\n<li> \r\nRequirements Analysis and Design Definition\r\n</li>\r\n<li> \r\nSolution Evaluation\r\n</li>\r\n<li> \r\nIntroduction to CCBA certification   \r\n</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'Total 3,750 hours of Business Analysis work experience in the last 7 years.\r\nOf these 3750 hours, 900 hours experience should be in at least 2 of the 6 knowledge areas defined in BABOK Guide, or\r\na minimum of 500 hours experience should be available in 4 of the 6 BABOK defined knowledge areas', 'The Certification of Capability in Business Analysis (CCBA) certification is designed to empower business analyst professionals, with cutting edge business analysis skills, trusted worldwide to devise perfect business solutions and produce reliable quality results. Based on the industry standards, the CCBA training and certification course help project managers, hybrid business managers recognize business requirements, manage stakeholder engagement, strategize and evaluate devised solutions to increase business efficiency and consistency.\r\n<br><br>\r\nDesigned by IIBA, CCBA certification is the', 'second level certification. Brillica Services offers official CCBA training curriculum through the CCBA certification training. Our master instructors help you acquire the business analysis proficiencies, prepare and pass the CCBA certification exam with striking scores and get your expertise recognized across worldwide.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Service’s CCBA training and certification course can be taken at any preferred location through blended modes, according to your convenience. Our readily available custom training solutions fit well into your schedules, help you acquire the critical business analysis skills, fulfil your learning needs and stay ahead of the curve.', '', 'Product Managers,\r\nNon-BA consultants,\r\nProject Testers,\r\nQuality Assurance (QA) professionals,\r\nChange/Transformation Managers, and Designers', 5, ''),
(20, 'ECBA Training', 'The Entry Certificate in Business Analysis™ (ECBA™) accredited by IIBM is amongst the most popular business analysis certification for beginners, willing to advance their career in business analysis domain.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>\r\nIntroduction to BABOK v3</li>\r\n<li>Problem Solving & Analytical thinking</li>\r\n<li>Understanding Software Development Process</li>\r\n<li>Software Development Methodologies (SDLCs)</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge area- Business Analysis </li>\r\n<li>Planning and Monitoring</li>\r\n<li>Concept of requirements</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge area- Elicitation and Collaboration</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge area- Requirements Analysis and Design Definition</li>\r\n<li>Requirements Modelling with UML</li>\r\nData Modelling</li>\r\n<li>Business Analysis Tools</li>\r\n<li>Preparing SRS Document</li>\r\n<li>Handling Requirements in Agile Projects</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge area- Requirement life cycle management</li>\r\n<li>Verification and Validation</li>\r\n<li>SQL for business analysts</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge Area – Strategy Analysis</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge Area – Solution Evaluation</li>\r\n<li>Project Assignments\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'For ECBA training, no official BA work experience is expected from the participants. However, from the ECBA certification exam perspective, you must possess 21 hours of professional development in the last 4 years and\r\nagree with the ECBA™ Code of Conduct', 'The Entry Certificate in Business Analysis™ (ECBA™) accredited by IIBM is amongst the most popular business analysis certification for beginners, willing to advance their career in business analysis domain. The ECBA certification course is designed to impart foundational business analysis knowledge and instil in the competencies of effective elicitation, collaboration, requirement analysis, planning and monitoring, essential to accomplish the defined business objectives.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services’ ECBA training and certification course empower you with the core business analysis skills, knowledge and behaviours that global organizations seek in practising ', 'business analysis professionals. Our experienced and certified instructors impart the ECBA certification mapped training based on the principles, knowledge areas and business analysis best practices defined in BABOK Guide. \r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services’ ECBA certification training courses encompass the functional, administrative, and technical aspects of business analysis management and target to refine your analyzing competencies. With a team of industry experienced instructors and proven records of delivering best-in-class ECBA training, we ensure to deliver a personalized learning experience with blended training modes and custom schedules.', '', 'All individuals and new graduates willing to step into the world of Business Analytics\r\nAll professionals seeking a career transition into business analysis, and\r\nall functional managers, managing a team of business analysts', 5, ''),
(21, 'PRINCE2 Foundation and Practitioner ', 'PRINCE2 stands for ‘Projects in Controlled Environments’. It is a unique and process-based project management approach. Being the de facto standard for project management practice in the United Kingdom and Europe, Prince2 Certification has gained popularity and is recognized across the globe and is available in Foundation and Practitioner levels', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li> Prince 2 Foundation Introduction</li>\r\n<li>Introduction To Prince 2\r\nPrinciples</li>\r\n<li>Process Model Overview</li>\r\n<li>Organisation</li>\r\n<li>Starting Up A Project</li>\r\n<li>Business Case</li>\r\n<li>Directing A Project</li>\r\n<li>Initiating A Project</li>\r\n<li>Risk</li>\r\n<li>Quality</li>\r\n<li>Plans</li>\r\n<li>Controlling A Stage</li>\r\n<li>Managing Product Delivery Mod 15 Progress</li>\r\n<li>Change</li>\r\n<li>Managing A Stage Boundary</li>\r\n<li>Prince 2 Foundation Outro</li>\r\n<li>Closing A Project  </li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'There are no pre-requisites to begin the PRINCE2® Foundation and Practitioner course. However, to enrol for the PRINCE2® Practitioner examination, PRINCE2® Foundation Exam should be completed and passed.\r\n\r\n', 'PRINCE2 stands for ‘Projects in Controlled Environments’. It is a unique and process-based project management approach. Being the de facto standard for project management practice in the United Kingdom and Europe, Prince2 Certification has gained popularity and is recognized across the globe and is available in Foundation and Practitioner levels. Gaining core knowledge of PRINCE2 principles helps you to develop and implement the product-based approach, while dividing the project into controllable chunks, to ensure successful project execution.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services is the authorized training provider of official Prince2 training', 'and certification course and envisions imparting PRINCE2 practice guidelines for managing project aspect such as Cost, Time, Quality, Scope and Risk with efficiency.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOur pool of certified and experienced instructors ensure to offer you the best-in-class Prince2 training and help you get acquaintance with the Prince2 methodology, terminology, principles, processes, themes and also gain real-time exposure to tackle actual industry scenarios with the help of live examples, assignments and projects. Blended learning modes and flexible schedules help you to fulfil all your training needs with many conveniences at affordable cost at Brillica Services, ensuring your certification journey to be an enriched one', '', 'Project Managers,\r\nTeam Leaders,\r\nProject Executives,\r\nProject Engineers,\r\nAssistant Project Managers,\r\nSoftware Developers,\r\nand Business Analyst.', 5, 'img/group 2311.png'),
(22, '\r\nITIL v4 Training', '\r\nThe augmented concentration of IT organizations on enhancing IT support in troubleshooting and managing services, improving employee throughput and accomplishing business goals has doubled the need and demand for gaining in-depth knowledge on ITIL (Information Technology Infrastructure Library) framework.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>\r\n\r\nIntroduction to ITIL v4</li>\r\n<li>High-Level Service Management and Introduction</li>\r\n<li>Where are Services and Service Management Today?</li>\r\n<li>Introduction to the Key Elements of ITIL 4\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nServices Defined\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nService Offerings and Relationships\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nService Relationship Model\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nDimensions of Service Management\r\n\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nValue Streams and Processes\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nITIL Service Value System\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nService Value System – Design and Transition\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nITIL’s 7 Guiding principles\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n\r\nIntroduction to Key ITIL Practices\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nGeneral Management Practices Purpose Statements\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nSMP Change Control The Definition\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nSMP Incident Management\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nProblem Management\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nSMP Service Requests Management \r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nService Level Management (SLM)\r\n\r\n</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'There are no official pre-requisite for taking the ITIL 4 Foundation Certification, yet familiarity with IT terminology and IT-related work experience are recommended.', 'The augmented concentration of IT organizations on enhancing IT support in troubleshooting and managing services, improving employee throughput and accomplishing business goals has doubled the need and demand for gaining in-depth knowledge on ITIL (Information Technology Infrastructure Library) framework. The ITIL 4 Foundation certification is the latest version that is globally recognized and encompasses IT service management standards that apply to organizations across industries and helps in offering quality-driven IT managed services.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services delivers all-embracing ITIL v4 Foundation certification training to the aspiring managers and team leads and helps them strengthen the fundamentals of IT services management principles, ', 'lifecycle, ITSM nomenclatures and best practices.  We bring on-board several years of expertise with the help of certified instructors to impart comprehensive knowledge on system support, management, and troubleshooting through real-time scenario-based ITIL v4 training and certification course.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAt Brillica Services, we strive to expand your technical knowledge of ITIL included concepts on service strategy, design, transition, operation, and fundamentals of CSI (continual service improvement) with ITIL v4 Foundational training course. Our customized learning solutions available in blended modes for ITIL v4 Foundation training is aimed to help service industry professionals to attain a firm understanding of the ITIL framework and IT service management principles on the go.\r\n\r\n', '', 'All Individuals who need to understand the refreshed ITIL framework and unearth how it can be used to enhance the quality of IT service management within an organization,\r\nall IT professionals associated with an organization that has adopted and adapted ITIL, who need to be informed about and thereafter contribute to, an ongoing service improvement program.\r\nThis may include but is not limited to, IT professionals, business managers and business process owners.', 5, 'img/group 2310.png'),
(23, '\r\nJava Web Development', 'Programming has the power to bring algorithms to life. Of most programming languages, Java is the utmost powerful and robust programming language that empowers programmers to develop engaging website interfaces and applications. Emerging from the wide applications, Java’s web development capability supports the creation of engaging, dynamic and responsive websites through servlets and JSPs.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>Fundamentals</li>\r\n<li>Pillars of Object-Oriented Programming</li>\r\n<li>Exception Handling</li>\r\n<li>File Input/Output</li>\r\n<li>Generics</li>\r\n<li>Mini Project-1</li>\r\n<li>\r\nNetwork Programming</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Introduction to RDBMS/MySQL</li>\r\n\r\n<li>JDBC</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Mini Project-2</li>\r\n<li> \r\nIntroduction to the Internet</li>\r\n<li> Architecting Java App</li>\r\n<li> HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>\r\n<li> Servlet, JSP</li>\r\n<li> Session Management</li>\r\n<li> Introduction to JMS, EJB, Web Services</li>\r\n<li> Mini Project-3\r\n  </li>\r\n<li>Enterprise Landscape</li>\r\n<li>Build tools: Maven</li>\r\n<li>Spring Core</li>\r\n<li>Spring MVC</li>\r\n<li>RESTful Webservices</li>\r\n<li>Responsive website development</li>\r\n<li>Spring Boot</li>\r\n<li>ORM: Hibernate</li>\r\n<li>Persistence with Spring </li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'There is no pre-requisite for this course. Prior exposure to object-oriented programming concepts is not required, but beneficial.', 'Programming has the power to bring algorithms to life. Of most programming languages, Java is the utmost powerful and robust programming language that empowers programmers to develop engaging website interfaces and applications. Emerging from the wide applications, Java’s web development capability supports the creation of engaging, dynamic and responsive websites through servlets and JSPs. \r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Sevices is a renowned provider of all-encompassing Java Web development training course to ', 'benefit beginner to advanced level Java as per the industrial requirement. The Java web development training spectrum includes spans across essential concepts including Java array, loops, functions, thread, servlets and services.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAt Brillica Services, we aim to deliver only the Java web development training and certification program in various learning modes and customized schedules. Our industry expert trainers have several years of professional experience and exceptional training skills. Register now to explore the world of web development with us!', '', 'Web Developers,\r\nWeb Designers,\r\nJava Developers,\r\nand Database Administrator.', 6, 'img/group 2309.png'),
(24, '\r\nFull Stack Development Certification', 'Full-stack development technology is the most comprehensive and complete in-house solution to develop engaging websites and applications for global enterprises. The Full Stack Development revolves around developing each layer of the software comprised of front-end, back-end, and the databases including all integral components such as UI and UX design, underlying platform and coding.\r\n\r\n', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>Introduction </li>\r\n\r\n<li>HTML Basics </li>\r\n<li>CSS </li>\r\n<li>JavaScript</li>\r\n<li>JavaScript Supported Data Structures </li>\r\n<li>Adv. JavaScript</li>\r\n<li>jQuery </li>\r\n<li>AJAX</li>\r\n<li>Jquery Animations</li>\r\n<li>HTML 5 </li>\r\n<li>CSS 3 </li>\r\n\r\n<li>Mongo DB </li>\r\n<li>Angular JS </li>\r\n<li>Node JS </li>\r\n<li>Express JS </li>\r\n</ul>', 'All individuals who want to become a Full Stack Developer,\r\nall Front-end developers who wish to acquire backend programming skills,\r\nand all Back-end developers who wish to acquire front-end programming skills.', 'Full-stack development technology is the most comprehensive and complete in-house solution to develop engaging websites and applications for global enterprises. The Full Stack Development revolves around developing each layer of the software comprised of front-end, back-end, and the databases including all integral components such as UI and UX design, underlying platform and coding.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFull Stack Development training and certification course at Brillica Services is designed to empower you with the critical skills ', 'to dev