(25, 'Blockchain Developer - Ethereum', 'The Certified Blockchain Developer – Ethereum certification course targets to help programmers and developers to delve into developing smart contracts on the most popular blockchain computing platform known as Ethereum, building Blockchain applications and interact with them seamlessly.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li> Blockchain and Smart Contract Basics\r\n</li>\r\n<li> Smart Contract Programming Basics\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Understanding Decentralized Information and Web3\r\n</li>\r\n<li> Basics of Ethereum and the EVM\r\n</li>\r\n<li> Solidity Advanced: Modifiers, Mappings, Structs and Inheritance\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Understanding Deployment and Costs\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Mining, Proof of Work vs. Proof of Authority\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Current Problems, Solutions, Outlook and Serenity\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Working in Teams, Testing and Versioning\r\n</li>\r\n<li> IPFS and distributed File-Storage\r\n</li>\r\n<li> Bonus Section: Compilation\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'It is highly important to have basic JavaScript and HTML knowledge. However, additional understanding of C++ and git repositories can help you have a cutting edge in grasping the concepts easily.', 'The Certified Blockchain Developer – Ethereum certification course targets to help programmers and developers to delve into developing smart contracts on the most popular blockchain computing platform known as Ethereum, building Blockchain applications and interact with them seamlessly.\r\n<br><br><br>\r\nBrillica Services is a renowned training partner to offer certification mapped CBDE (Certified Blockchain Developer- Ethereun) training to help developers design decentralized applications after understanding the Ethereum architecture and Solidity language. ', 'Our certified and experienced instructors help you master development of all functional Ethereum components and instantiate the developed application on the enterprise network.\r\n<br><br><Br>\r\nThe official CBDE Certification curriculum imparting in-depth understanding on how transactions are created and implemented on Ethereum network is offered at Brillica Services in diverse blended modes and at custom schedules to meet your specific learning goals at affordable costs.\r\n\r\n', '', 'Programmers,\r\nApplication Developers,\r\nSystem Architects,\r\nNetwork Architects,\r\nNetwork Security Architects, and\r\nIT Professionals w/programming experience.', 7, 'img/group 2307.png'),
(26, 'CBDH Training', 'The Certified Blockchain Developer Hyperledger Fabric (CBDH) certification evaluates your Hyperledger Fabric development skills, knowledge and competency at developing production-ready applications for the Hyperledger Blockchain.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>  \r\nCertified Blockchain Developer Hyperledger</li>\r\n<li>How does a Blockchain Works</li>\r\n<li>Blockchain Architecture Review\r\n   </li>\r\n<li>Hyperledger Project Overview</li>\r\n<li>Hyperledger Framework Comparisons</li>\r\n<li>Hyperledger Fabric</li>\r\n<li>Hyperledger Fundamentals and Components</li>\r\nHyperledger Transactions</li>\r\n<li> Deploying Hyperledger Fabric on a BaaS</li>\r\n<li>Installing Hyperledger Fabric</li>\r\n<li>Hyperledger Fabric Explorer</li>\r\n<li>Hyperledger Composer</li>\r\n<li> Hyperledger Development</li>\r\n<li>Bootstrapping </li>\r\n</ul>', 'It is highly important to have basic JavaScript and HTML knowledge. However, additional understanding of C++ and git repositories can help you attain a cutting-edge and grasp the concepts easily.', 'The Certified Blockchain Developer Hyperledger Fabric (CBDH) certification evaluates your Hyperledger Fabric development skills, knowledge and competency at developing production-ready applications for the Hyperledger Blockchain.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services is an accredited training provider of an array of Blockchain training and certification courses including Certified Blockchain Developer Hyperledger Fabric (CBDH). The course provides you with an across-the-board knowledge and practical exposure on developing a decentralized Blockchain solution for verifying and tracking cryptocurrency and digital transactions.', 'Our large pool of experienced and certified instructors help you emerge as fine blockchain developers and technical leaders. The hands-on practical exposure provided during the CBDH training, helps you build expertise at selecting best-fit Hyperledger Blockchain systems for different use cases, write, test and implement flawless chain codes. \r\n<br><br>\r\nThe CBDH training course at Brillica Services is made available to you in diverse modes at flexible schedules and affordable training cost, to map your unique learning requirements seamlessly.', '', 'Programmers,\r\nDevelopers,\r\nSoftware Engineers,\r\nand application architects.', 7, 'img/group 2306.png'),
(27, '\r\nCertified Blockchain Foundation', 'Blockchain technology- an ingenious invention has emerged to be the most sought-after skill over the years. Originally devised for cryptocurrencies, the experts have found potential technology uses and it now offers intuitive features of utmost security, immutability, decentralization and high transparency.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>  Origin And Working Of Blockchain</li>\r\n<li>Intro To Blockchain And Cryptocurrency </li>\r\n<li>Clearing And Settlement </li>\r\n<li>Ethereum And Blockchain Platforms </li>\r\n<li>Bitcoin Mining </li>\r\n<li>Basic Solidity </li>\r\n<li>Advanced Solidity </li>\r\n<li>Hyperledger </li>\r\n<li>Create And Deploy Your Private Blockchain On MultiChain </li>\r\n<li>Assets And Tokenization And The Value Of The Blockchain </li>\r\n<li>Your First Wallet And Intro To Blockchain API </li>\r\n<li>Prospects Of Blockchain </li>\r\n<li>Smart Contracts </li>\r\n<li>Regulatory Environment </li>\r\n<li>Use Cases </li>\r\n<li>Security: Attacks and Trust-Less Networks  </li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'A sufficient understanding of programming is expected from the candidates who wish to take Blockchain training and certification course. Though not mandatory, it would be an advantage if you have a basic understanding of\r\n linux Fundamentals,\r\nJS Basic Understanding and\r\nJava Script', 'Blockchain technology- an ingenious invention has emerged to be the most sought-after skill over the years. Originally devised for cryptocurrencies, the experts have found potential technology uses and it now offers intuitive features of utmost security, immutability, decentralization and high transparency.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services is a premium IT training company, an IBM accredited authorized partner to deliver Blockchain Foundation training and certification course. It encompasses a broad technology spectrum providing insights on Bitcoin, cryptocurrencies fundamentals,', 'Blockchain tools, platforms. The comprehensive training is delivered by experienced and certified instructors who help you imbibe deep understanding on how to set up a private Blockchain using Multichain platform and cover the practical use cases of Blockchain in various industries.\r\n<br><br><br>\r\nAs a definitive introduction to Blockchain, our Certified Blockchain foundation course is ideal for both the developer and non-developer learners. Brillica Services also offer you customized training in different modes at convenient schedules to map your learning requirements.\r\n\r\n', '', 'Program Developers,\r\nProject Managers,\r\nTechnical Solution Architects,\r\nTechnical Support Personals,\r\nBusiness Analyst,\r\n and Product Leader can opt for this course.', 7, 'img/group 2305.png'),
(28, 'CBSA Training', 'Certified Blockchain Solution Architect (CBSA) certification is a prominent way to validate your expert skills in Blockchain technology and emerge as a leader. The Certified Blockchain Solution Architect training and certification course equips you with the in-demand skills and desired expertise at making decisions for Blockchain Project, craft guidelines, design, develop, test and architect Blockchain solutions considering system requirements.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>\r\nWhat is Blockchain?</li>\r\n<li>Blockchain Basic Principles</li>\r\n<li>Centralized and Decentralized Ledgers</li>\r\n<li>Mechanics of Blockchain</li>\r\n<li>What is a Block?</li>\r\n<li>How are Blocks Chained Together?\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nBenefits and Drawbacks of Blockchain\r\n<li>Cryptography</li>\r\n<li>Public Key Cryptography</li>\r\n<li>Cryptographic Hashing</li>\r\n<li>Blockchain Consensus</li>\r\n<li>Proof of Work Consensus</li>\r\n<li>Proof of Stake Consensus</li>\r\n<li>Other Consensus Mechanisms Explained</li>\r\n<li>The lifecycle of a Public Blockchain</li>\r\n <li>Transaction\r\n</li>\r\n<li> Blockchain Application Architecture</li>\r\n<li>Integrated Development Environment (IDE)</li>\r\n<li>User Interaction Layer</li>\r\n<li>Middle/Interface Layer</li>\r\n<li>Smart Contracts/Chaincode </li>\r\n</ul>', 'It is recommended to possess basic knowledge of Blockchain and underlying platforms, which would help in grasping the included concepts in a better way. It would give you an added advantage if you have hands-on experience over the technology as well, though not mandatory.\r\n\r\n', 'Certified Blockchain Solution Architect (CBSA) certification is a prominent way to validate your expert skills in Blockchain technology and emerge as a leader. The CBSA training and certification course equips you with the in-demand skills and desired expertise at making decisions for Blockchain Project, craft guidelines, design, develop, test and architect Blockchain solutions considering system requirements.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Services offers extensive Blockchain Solution Architect training to help Blockchain engineers and developers to gain in-depth insights on the trending Blockchain technology, cryptocurrency basics,', 'various Blockchain tools, implementation and transition strategies and platforms to ensure delivery of flawless Blockchain solutions to the organizations.\r\n<br><br>\r\nOur certified and experienced instructors help you gain a comprehensive understanding of the most sought-after Blockchain architecting skills and familiarize you to real-time Blockchain tools and the right approach to set up a private Blockchain using multichain platform. The CBSA training course at Brillica Services is made available at custom schedules and diverse learning modes, leveraging you the opportunity to study at your preferences.', '', 'Blockchain Engineers,\r\nBlockchain analysts,\r\nApplication Developers,\r\nSolution Architect,\r\nProduct managers, ICT Professionals, Monetary Authority Professionals\r\nOperations and technology specialists\r\nDatabase Administrators, and\r\nEntrepreneur.', 7, 'img/group 2304.png'),
(29, '\r\nIBM- SPSS Training', 'The IBM SPSS® is the most robust statistical data analysis software that helps in turning crucial business data into actionable insights, forming a base for making critical business decisions. The vast machine learning algorithm library, specialized text analysis tools, high -extensibility, strong integration with big data helps in executing all levels of research projects efficiently.', '<ul type=\"disc\"> <li>Instructor-led Classroom and Online</li> <li>Training modes</li> <li>Best-in-Class Training Curriculum</li> <li>Beginner to Expert Level Training</li> <li>Hands-on Programming Practice</li> <li>Pro-Python Tips & Tricks Practice Activities</li> <li>Unlimited Access - Online or Offline Flexible Guaranteed to Run Schedules</li> <li>Self-Paced Learning</li> </ul>', '<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li>  Defining variables and entering data using the built-in Data Editor</li>\r\n<li>Applying dictionary information from another file</li>\r\n<li>Importing data from spreadsheets and other applications</li>\r\n<li>\r\nComputing new variables and recording data values</li>\r\n<li>Selecting subsets of the data</li>\r\n<li>Splitting data files to obtain sub-group summaries\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\nLevels of measurement (types of data)\r\nSummarizing variables using frequencies and descriptives</li>\r\n<li>Bar charts, histograms and boxplots\r\nSummaries of central tendency (e.g. mean, median and mode)</li>\r\n<li>Summaries of spread and shape (e.g. standard deviation, skewness)</li>\r\n<li>The ‘normal distribution’ and its importance</li>\r\n<li>Producing cross tabulation tables and testing for significant relationships with chi-square</li>\r\n<li>Assessing relationships between continuous variables through plots and correlations\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Basic knowledge of Computer handling and Statistics are sufficient to learn SPSS.', 'The IBM SPSS® is the most robust statistical data analysis software that helps in turning crucial business data into actionable insights, forming a base for making critical business decisions. The vast machine learning algorithm library, specialized text analysis tools, high -extensibility, strong integration with big data helps in executing all levels of research projects efficiently.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n The IBM SPSS training and certification courses help you equip with comprehensive analytical skills, essential to tap the growing career opportunities in data mining and research industry.Brillica Services specializes to deliver across the board understanding on IBM ', 'SPSS software and help you gain hands-on experience on creating charts and graphs, importing spreadsheets, analyzing data statistically, building reports, applying statistical testing, creating regression models and much more.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBrillica Service’s IBM SPSS training courses delivered by certified skilled instructors prepare you for a promising career in statistical analysis and research. Our flexible schedules blended with diverse training modes are aligned to map your learning needs\r\n\r\n', '', 'Statistician,\r\nData Analyst,\r\nBusiness Information Analyst,\r\nResearch Analyst,\r\nBusiness Analytics Consultant\r\nand Statistical Modeler.', 7, 'img/group 2303.png'),
